#### [MODIFY] [DocumentController.java](file:///d:/SWP391/backend/src/main/java/com/example/keeper/systems/document/controller/DocumentController.java)

Thêm API endpoint `/api/documents/recommended`:
```java
    @GetMapping("/recommended")
    public List<DocumentResponse> getRecommended(
            @RequestParam(defaultValue = "5") int limit) {
